snippet.title: Naughty Kitties Trailer
snippet.description: Naughty Kitties is our newest game and is released both on iOS and Google Play. Average rating over 4.7/5 in beta testing. A hybrid of defense and shooting game. The main character is cat, super cute cat. Enjoy!
